# DiffDrone Multi-Agent Configuration
# DiffDrone 多智能体训练配置
#
# This configuration is optimized for multi-agent quadrotor training.
# Use this configuration when training multiple quadrotors to
# coordinate through obstacles and complete tasks together.
#
# 该配置针对多智能体四轴飞行器训练进行了优化。
# 在训练多个四轴飞行器协同穿越障碍物完成任务时使用此配置。

# Add gate task / 添加门任务
# When enabled, adds gate obstacles that quadrotors must fly through
# 启用时，添加门障碍物，四轴飞行器必须穿过
# Gates consist of 4 vertical cylindrical posts forming a square opening
# 门由4个垂直圆柱形支柱组成，形成方形开口
# Requires coordination and precise flight control
# 需要协调和精确的飞行控制
--gate

# Collision loss weight / 碰撞损失权重
# Multi-agent collision detection includes:
# 多智能体碰撞检测包括：
# - Obstacle collisions (same as single-agent)
# - 障碍物碰撞（与单智能体相同）
# - Agent-agent collisions (new for multi-agent)
# - 智能体间碰撞（多智能体新增）
# Typical range: 5.0 - 10.0 for multi-agent scenarios
--coef_collide 5.0

# Obstacle avoidance loss weight / 避障损失权重
# Multi-agent requires more sophisticated avoidance:
# 多智能体需要更复杂的避障：
# - Avoid static obstacles
# - 避开静态障碍物
# - Avoid other agents in the same group
# - 避开同组中的其他智能体
# - Coordinate paths to prevent congestion
# - 协调路径以防止拥堵
# Typical range: 2.0 - 5.0
--coef_obj_avoidance 2.0

# Batch size / 批次大小
# Multi-agent training requires larger batch sizes for two reasons:
# 多智能体训练需要更大的批次大小，原因有二：
# 1. More agents per batch (e.g., 256 agents = 32 groups of 8)
# 每批更多智能体（例如：256个智能体 = 32组，每组8个）
# 2. Better gradient estimation for complex multi-agent dynamics
# 为复杂的多智能体动力学提供更好的梯度估计
# Recommended: 256 for multi-agent
--batch 256

# Horizontal field of view / 水平视场角
# Same meaning as single-agent config, but wider FOV is beneficial
# 与单智能体配置含义相同，但更宽的视场对多智能体有益
# for:
# 用于：
# - Seeing other agents in the group
# - 看到组中的其他智能体
# - Better coordination through visual information
# - 通过视觉信息更好地协调
--fov_x_half_tan 0.82

# Number of timesteps per episode / 每个episode的时间步数
# Multi-agent tasks are more complex and require more time:
# 多智能体任务更复杂，需要更多时间：
# - Coordination takes time to learn
# - 协调需要时间学习
# - Agents need to wait for each other
# - 智能体需要互相等待
# - Gate flying requires precise timing
# - 穿门需要精确的时机
# Typical range: 180 - 300 for complex multi-agent tasks
--timesteps 180
